e, live activity · elapsed time, and [✗] close button.\\n\\n/private/var/folders/rb/bzdrr2hj3x7db9mrc56chs440000gn/T/.tmpFSxEpj/.grok-home/docs/user-guide/17-sessions.md\\n39:`summary.json` is the index entry. It records the session summary and generated title, the model ID, the creation and update timestamps, the message counts, and a parent session reference for forked or restored s [... truncated (3773 chars total)]\n{\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"tool_call_id\":\"call-fecf24c5-330f-420e-9a09-2c1b193b7c8a-7\",\"content\":\"1→# Compaction Segment Index\\n\\n| Segment | File | Turns | Approx bytes | Keywords |\\n|---|---|---|---|---|\\n| 000 | segment_000.md | 4 | 24257 | \\\"Producing\\\", \\\"conversation\\\", \\\"compaction\\\", \\\"actions\\\", \\\"commands\\\", \\\"present\\\", \\\"visible\\\", \\\"transcript\\\" |\\n\"}\n{\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"id\":\"rs_4e19d4e4-f4dc-9902-84bb-e1638d9c655e\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"The user forked the session with directive \\\"continue here\\\". Looking at the workspace - it's almost empty, just a README.md. The previous session summary said there was no clear prior task. Let me dig ...\"}],\"encrypted_content\":\"\",\"status\":\"completed\"}\n{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"\",\"tool_calls\":[{\"id\":\"call-369bdee3-231b-41fd-bc48-a85772299df4-9\",\"name\":\"read_file\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"target_file\\\":\\\"/private/var/folders/rb/bzdrr2hj3x7db9mrc56chs440000gn/T/.tmpFSxEpj/.grok-home/docs/user-guide/04-slash-commands.md\\\",\\\"offset\\\":71,\\\"limit\\\":30}\"},{\"id\":\"call-369bdee3-231b-41fd-bc48-a85772299df4-10\",\"name\":\"read_file\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"target_file\\\":\\\"/private/var/folders/rb/bzdrr2hj3x7db9mrc56chs440000gn/T/.tmpFSxEpj/README.md\\\"}\"},{\"id\":\"call-369bdee3-231b-41fd-bc48-a85772299df4-11\",\"name\":\"list_dir\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"target_directory\\\":\\\"/private/var/folders/rb/bzdrr2hj3x7db9mrc56chs440000gn/T/.tmpFSxEpj/.grok-home/sessions\\\"}\"},{\"id